channel.title: A Bit More Backendy on Laura Kalbag

item.title: Guest on A Bit More Backendy podcast
item.description: Yesterday the fourth episode of the Backendy podcast was released, and I was the guest. It was lovely talking to Darren, partly because he’s been a great client for a while now, partly because I’ve been working on the podcast logo and site, and also because I think a podcast focusing on back-end development is a really good idea.
